    "body": "> Can you try to import from dist-es5-modules and tell me the result?\r\n\r\n@iam4x yep, that's what I'm doing right now, and it works. I just need to exclude it from my `babel-loader`, or I get errors.\r\n\r\nHowever, as I'm already compiling with webpack/babel, ideally I still want to import the ES6 modules. Why? For one, [tree shaking](http://jakewiesler.com/tree-shaking-es6-modules-in-webpack-2/).",
