    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It's recommended to exclude any libraries from `node_modules` into babel-loader comfiguration, this is an expected behaviour.\r\n\r\nAnd yes when transpiling from ES6 to ES5 with `babel-present-env` and `modules: false` like @Haroenv said only the imports/exports are kept es6.",
